{
  "texts": [
    "This uncertainty makes it hard to ensure that students are following these guidelines, and it is equally difficult to make sure that nobody is gaining an unfair advantage.",
    "Moreover, a significant number of students may not be fully aware of how to responsibly use AI tools, nor understand their limitations.",
    "This lack of knowledge can result in a reliance on AI-generated content without critical evaluation, potentially undermining the quality and integrity of academic work.",
    "At the same time, students might also miss out on the opportunity to enhance their learning and critical thinking skills through the proper use of AI.",
    "None of this can be remedied by simply providing a document and hoping that students would read it and abide by its ideals."
  ]
}